    "Generally, we categorize these strategies into two classes based on whether they require fine-tuning of the LLMs.",
    "In the following, we introduce each of them more in detail.Capability acquisition with fine-tuning: A straightforward method to enhance the agent capability for task completion is fine-tuning the agent based on task-dependent datasets.",
